<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910305-0121</DOCNO><DOCID>910305-0121.</DOCID><HL>   Hudson's Bay Extends Offer</HL><DATE>03/05/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C19</SO><CO>   T.HBC</CO><IN>BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)BROADLINE RETAILERS, DEPARTMENT STORES (RTB)</IN><LP>   TORONTO -- Hudson's Bay Co. said it extended to March 15its offer to purchase all its cumulative redeemable preferredshares Series A at 20.75 Canadian dollars (U.S.$18.01) ashare. The offer was to have expired yesterday.   About 1.9 million of the 3.6 million shares have beenrepurchased under the offer so far, the Toronto retailersaid.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>